# Keep the build context minimal and reproducible: never copy local build outputs, VCS history, secrets,
# persisted runs, or packaged artifacts into the image. Only source needed to restore+publish is sent.
**/bin/
**/obj/
artifacts/
**/runs/
.git/
.github/
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/.audit/
**/*.env
*.pfx
*.key
*.pem
secrets*.json
principals*.json
